musicInfo.artist_name: Ram Sampath, Arijit Singh, Prashant Pandey

latestPosts.caption:
Dancing on this immensely beautiful song, on the stage after very long, to be precise after 6 long years!! 
Yes I was nervous, it can show on my face expressions as well. 
I felt as if I had forgotten the entire choreography, but all’s well that ends well✨
Making dance videos and performing on the stage are two very different things, and I am so delighted to be back on the stage. It was truly a lovely and significant experience, and I absolutely loved myself up there🦋.

Thank you @yashtumane for this opportunity and this adorable choreography🫶🏻.

(Stage performance, dance, semi classical, dancing girl)
